---
title: Millionaire's Cheesecake Christmas Puddings with Salted Caramel and Almonds
description: Something sweet for afters! This indulgent festive dessert is a twist on the classic Millionaire's shortbread, combining layers of crunchy speculoos biscuit crumb, dark chocolate cheesecake filling and smooth salted caramel. A final sprinkling of flaked almonds make this a very merry Christmas pudding.
